==English==
===Etymology===
Latin '''[[torridus]]''', from '''[[torrere]]''' 'parch, scorch'.

===Adjective===
'''torrid''' ('''more torrid''', '''most torrid''')
# Very [[hot]] and [[dry]].
# Full of intense emotions arising from sexual love; [[ardent]] and [[passionate]].
# Full of [[difficulty]].

====Derived terms====
*[[torrid zone]]

===Quote===
"Lita and I are going to have live torrid sex in the middle of the ring, live on RAW."
- Edge, after winning the WWE Title from John Cena at New Year's Revolution.

